{"tid":1593134,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"旺角警署防暴警凌晨清場","createTime":"2019-09-25T02:42:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T02:46:30.000Z","uid":101310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2ebb151ef80f2ce9c8363c18357e13021cf7ac58","tid":1593134,"uid":101310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T02:42:50.000Z","msg":"反修訂《逃犯條例》風波未息，自警方8月31日晚在港鐵太子站內行動，警方及消防先後澄清「打死人」傳言，惟市民持續在太子站外獻花拜祭。昨晚（24日）再有市民在旺角警署外聚集抗議、上香，高唱諷刺警察的歌曲及用激光筆照向警署。<br />\n<br />\n市民與警方對峙至凌晨1時許，警方突然從旺角警署樓上舉藍旗，同時大批防暴警從水馬後衝出，市民四散，其間警方制服3人，又於附近街道截查7人，警方把10人全數拘捕帶走。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UpHd73U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUpHd73U.jpg&h=1ad5d1ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e10ff63991d80db05a4feff42dfa13d34f81fee","tid":1593134,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T02:43:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚癲，香港冇大台運動，已經發展到929全球冇大台反支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592119</a>"},{"pid":"c30bb6d321c625c3cabaa85c90271267c7fe6163","tid":1593134,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T02:46:30.000Z","msg":"［警世］有無人記得當年文宣遍地開花既盛況<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1593125\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1593125</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}